Interface EddReadable

All Known Subinterfaces:
IEdd
All Known Implementing Classes:
ExperimentDesignDetails
public interface EddReadable
Readable (immutable) interface for ExperimentDesignDetails. This is the only access to this class by any other class.

    • getFactors

      Map<String,​ExpFactor> getFactors()
      Returns a read-only (immutable) map of experiment factors (ExpFactor). The map 'key' is the alias name of the factor, that is the edge Id between the Treatment node and the Field being manipulated in the configuration graph.
      Returns:
      an Immutable map of ExpFactor.

    • getTreatments

      List<List<au.edu.anu.rscs.aot.graph.property.Property>> getTreatments()
      Returns a read-only (immutable) list of properties: one list for each simulator. Each simulation sets its property (constants) values to the properties in the list after initialization.
      Returns:
      Immutable list of Properties and their values.

    • getBaseline

      Map<String,​Object> getBaseline()
      Returns a read-only (immutable) list of simulator constants. This list is built by the simulator when first initialized. The values may be subsequently changed by the experiment treatments following initialization.
      Returns:
      Immutable list of baseline values for these simulators.
